    "nl/) into the research pipeline of a systematic review, researchers must first install the software.",
    "Once installed, the program can be operated via a web browser's graphical user interface (GUI).",
    "To initiate the abstract screening process, a project folder is created in the ASReview GUI, and the study database, including at least the titles and abstracts of the searched studies, must be added.",
    "The study database can be stored in different data formats, such as.csv,.txt, or.xlsx.",
    "ASReview runs locally on the computer, so the information is not shared with others or stored on external servers."
